tags.description:
Parsing a basic JSON file

Contents of `file.json`
```json
{
  "exampleItem": "text"
}
```

Usage
```ts
const result = parseFile("file.json");
```

Result
```ts
{
  exampleItem: 'text',
}
```

annotation.returns: An object containing the JSON data.
